<br>
Level of pet : 60<br>
Max hit : 81<br>
Delay : 17 <br>
Casts : some ice spell DD<br>
Max backstab : 241<br>
Special Abilities : Pet regens 3 %  / tick<br>
Special Abilities : Pet enrages at 10 %  Rate lasts 10 secconds<br>
<br>
<br>
(definately hits faster then epic, and has more DPS even WITHOUGH a DS then epic,  hits for max more often then epic aswell)<br>
<br>
Additional info : the pet does not tank near aswell as epic, nor does he casts stuns (which helps in tanking)  howerver with Aegolism, he stood up prety damn well againsts mobs that were hitting for 300's.  You COULD use this pet in a mage / cleric  duo, however I see it hard to use this guy solo, he's best for HIGH  DPS in groups or  HIGH  DPS and regen abilities in farming greens.<br>
